                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8133" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1255</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1779 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">传统珠宝企业Q公司的数字化转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital transformation of traditional jewellery company Q</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨骏，宋娟如，任钰琪，贺倩，李琦</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长安大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王丽萍，夏明学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陕西群鑫实业发展有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">传统珠宝企业；数字化；战略转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> traditional jewelry business, digitalisation, strategic transformation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例以传统珠宝企业Q公司的发展历程为时间轴线进行写作，客观真实地记录了从2003年中国黄金珠宝市场开放到2022年疫情退却这段特殊的岁月里，Q公司是如何抓住机会，迎难而上，变革进取，最终化解重重危机完成蜕变的企业奋斗史。 在这一过程中案例重点介绍了Q公司在2020-2022年具体通过优化结构体系、搭建数字平台和开展数字营销实现了传统珠宝企业的数字化转型升级。本案例通过对Q公司发展历程的深度研究，一方面可以让学生真切感受到企业经营之所以困难是因为其所处的外部环境复杂多变。如何辨识环境，适应环境并改善环境是管理者必须具备的基本素养。另一方面加深学生对理论知识指导实践重要作用的认知。Q公司每一次危机的化解都是在科学管理理论的指导下进行的，因此管理学、市场营销等经典理论知识的学习至关重要。最后面对科技发展的日新月异，消费者主权时代的到来，传统企业一定要打破常规，与时俱进，才能不断焕发新的活力与可持续发展的动力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> This case takes the development history of traditional jewellery enterprise Q Company as the time axis for writing, objectively and truthfully records how Q Company seizes the opportunity, rises to the challenge, changes and forges ahead, and ultimately resolves the crises to complete the transformation of the enterprise&#39;s struggle in the special years from the opening of China&#39;s gold and jewellery market in 2003 to the receding of the epidemic in 2022. In this process, the case focuses on the digital transformation and upgrading of the traditional jewellery company by optimising the structural system, building a digital platform and carrying out digital marketing in 2020-2022. Through the in-depth study of the development history of Company Q, the case can make students feel that the reason why the business is difficult is because of the complexity and change of the external environment in which it is located. How to identify the environment, adapt to the environment and improve the environment is the basic quality that managers must have. On the other hand, it can deepen students&#39; knowledge of the importance of theoretical knowledge to guide practice. every crisis of Q Company is solved under the guidance of scientific management theories, so the study of classical theories such as management science and marketing is of vital importance. Finally, in the face of the rapid development of science and technology, the arrival of the era of consumer sovereignty, traditional enterprises must break the routine, keep pace with the times, in order to continue to revitalise the new vitality and sustainable development of the power.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化转型；价值链模型；AARRR漏斗模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
